{"tid":1777192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和人展］工展會副會長：強調工展會不能阻止警方進場執法！！！","createTime":"2019-12-10T05:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T07:33:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7d78130918b40771b788b4ddb14840dff6488b89","tid":1777192,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"工展會第一天開鑼，有網民計劃於黃昏時段發起「和你展」活動。廠商會第二副會長兼展覽服務有限公司主席徐晉暉形容，工展會是「香港人的工展會」，對活動表示歡迎，不過呼籲參與人士不要對其他市民造成太大滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n徐晉暉指，沒有就網民計劃的活動特別向警方作出相應協調，不過他提到，過往有扒手出現工展會會場時，也會有警員進入會場範圍，強調今屆工展會也不能阻止警方進場執法。<br />\n<br />\n若果展覽期間交通狀況有異，他希望相關政府部門可以協助疏導人群。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496911-20191210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496911-20191210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0302b344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496911-20191210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=45cf4900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496911-20191210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a8c4f6db8af462f024f263e0902f526c0391179a","tid":1777192,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"05d41196bafb19744184a197c41236d4bd9197b6","tid":1777192,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s